# Self-hosted web fonts belong here.
#
# Prefer .woff2 (smallest, best supported). Reference them from
# /assets/css/main.css with an @font-face block and set the --font-sans
# custom property to the new family. Self-hosting (rather than Google Fonts)
# avoids a third-party request and is faster for Core Web Vitals.
#
# This file only exists so Git tracks the otherwise-empty folder. It can be
# deleted once real font files are added.
